    Extract information from DIA-NN logs

    readDIANNInfo.Rd

    Read DIA-NN log file and extract information about the run.

    readDIANNInfo(diannLog)

    Arguments

    diannLog

    Character scalar, the path to a log file from a DIA-NN run.

    Value

    A list with extracted information about the DIA-NN run.

    Author

    Charlotte Soneson

    Examples

    readDIANNInfo(system.file("extdata", "diann_example",
                          "diann-output.log.txt",
                          package = "einprot"))
